  "texts": [
    "In this paper, we have set out to better understand how different stakeholders establish their vision of AI as a key sociotechnical phenomenon.",
    "Since this varies greatly across different regions and countries, we have addressed this by comparing China, the U.S. and Germany as particularly interesting and differing cases.",
    "The analysis confirms previous general findings of corporate dominance in AI discourse and development, yet this does not occur uniformly across all countries and themes.",
    "In the U.S., the discourse differs across several geographic AI centres.",
    "The German case reveals a strong focus on EU policy compliance and displayed distinct geographical distributions by stakeholders with different AI imaginaries."
  ],
